org.ojai

Interface DocumentStream<T extends Document>

  • All Superinterfaces:
    AutoCloseable, Iterable<T>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    JsonDocumentStream

    @API.Public
public interface DocumentStream<T extends Document>
extends AutoCloseable, Iterable<T>
    A stream of documents. Implements Iterable but only one call is allows to iterator() or readerIterator(). Only one of these iterators can be retrieved from the stream.
